1 A. The maximum rebates that may be paid pursuant to the
2 provisions of this act shall not exceed Ten Million Dollars
3 ($10,000,000.00) each fiscal year.
4 B. The maximum rebate that may be paid to a business entity
5 with respect to a single event at an eligible venue shall be Two
