4 levy occurring during the period of time beginning twelve (12) hours
5 prior to the scheduled start time for a musical performance at the
6 eligible venue and ending twelve (12) hours after the scheduled
7 start time for a musical performance at the eligible venue.
8 D. An eligible venue entity may apply for a rebate of either
9 sales tax or mixed beverage gross receipts tax or both such taxes
10 according to the provisions of this act no more often than quarterly
11 during each calendar year. The application shall be submitted to
12 the Oklahoma Tax Commission no later than the following dates:
13 1. April 20 for the First Quarter;
14 2. July 20 for the Second Quarter;
15 3. October 20 for the Third Quarter; and
16 4. January 20 of the succeeding calendar year for the Fourth
17 Quarter.
